Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:34.49,Takagi san—Picture 10-1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1446,804)}新年参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:14.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,同乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,圣诞节你送我的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:35.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你送我的围巾也很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  和家人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他们在和熟人聊天  看样子要聊上很久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  我们家也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  一起参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:02:59.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,人还挺多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是元旦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽说很正常  但全是一家子或者情侣一起来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我俩啥也不是  总觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个  我记得是二行礼二拍手一行礼对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好像没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望今年不被高木同学捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你许了什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没什么  保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望不被我捉弄之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哈哈  我猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  已经被她捉弄上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学许了什么愿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,保密  你猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正就是希望能捉弄我之类的呗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:11.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就算不许愿也能捉弄到你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  来比今年第一场比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:30.62,Takagi san—Picture 10-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz271.2\move(978.667,453.333,1018.667,453.333,0,4824)}神签
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:30.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们比抽签  运势好的人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  谁能赢全凭运气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:38.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年伊始  我要改变被捉弄的运势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  我接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看她这从容不迫的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:49.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要抽个好签  一定要赢过你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来吧  大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吉还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好像仅次于大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,应该比中吉小吉要好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  只要高木同学抽不到大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就至少是平手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:19.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,请给我两份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一共400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:36.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望身体健康？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的是我许愿的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  大好新年竟然屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都要猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我妈妈打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我正在喝甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:06.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起  家人叫我了  我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  还想和我再待一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  也不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,, 我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年第一次比赛也赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,和你见面真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明年的抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一定会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你的意思是明年也要一起新年参拜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  要是能偶遇的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,希望明年也能和你一起新年参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  明年也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正每年我爸妈都会和熟人聊上半天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没想到愿望这么快就实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:14.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我许的愿望是希望西片再找我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说  你肯定说谎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.97,Takagi san—Picture 10-3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,450)\pos(490,400)}雪  人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,积雪了  积雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.28,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.472\move(1390,550,1448,548,0,2030)\fs50\t(0,2030,\fs55)}收到新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.28,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.472\move(1054,672,1064,684,0,2030)\fs50\t(0,2030,\fs55)}滑动显示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好啊  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  西片  真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:02.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是因为积雪了所以兴高采烈的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没啊  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:09.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过积雪确实很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:14.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  我记得已经五年没有积这么多雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,额  我可没有兴高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.52,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.53\an1\fs40\pos(402,396)}要不要现在\N去空地比赛堆雪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.52,Takagi san—Picture 10-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.53\fs40\pos(688,490)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说赶紧开始吧  这个所谓的堆雪人比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是呢  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为会被雪弄湿  所以今天我戴了这双手套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,厚手套吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,估计她以为这样就能赢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:49.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太天真了  太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为我很擅长堆大雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只不过  最后一次堆还是在上小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,时限三十分钟  不能使用工具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后  谁能堆出更好的雪人就算赢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:08.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的雪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是大的雪人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个怎么判断啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们相互打分评定呗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还以为是比大小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底是什么才是好的雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦  也可以把大小算到分数里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她肯定是故意没说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,艺术分和尺寸分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,靠综合评分来定胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:57.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  总之堆个大的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我就先去拿一下材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很从容啊  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,时间可只有三十分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:15.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样弄  尽量把中心弄得硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好  很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再做大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她怕了  她怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:36.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没想到我能堆这么大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:40.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,身体做这么大应该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下面该做头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  看看高木同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很有雪人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,赢了的话要让你干什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再大  再大些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:26.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,必杀  滚雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还剩一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个大小怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然弄脏了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是这大小  肯定会比高木同学的雪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还剩三十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  先把雪人堆完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想想也是 滚起来都够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还剩15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟西片的雪人都没堆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感觉就算完成了也赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用了  重得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且我都输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难得堆一次雪人  堆完它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完成了也赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感觉好像情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  这不是更像父母与孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:32.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,请我喝热饮吧  无关胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哈？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.51,Takagi san—Picture 10-5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1466,400)}正月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好像看起来更霸气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个正月我在钻研新的技艺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新的技艺？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早餐吃30个年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:05.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吃得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,祝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,觉得好怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,贺年卡都写了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有必要这样问好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这种仪式很重要的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看  不是有谚语这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一富士二鹰三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不四处问好会被五寸钉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这可是新年  按仪式做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么正月会结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我还想多过一会儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  你们正月都干嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,放风筝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩和歌纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩双六
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟亲戚们玩的可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是中学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗你都干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一直在跑步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是田径部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在亲戚家之间来回奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到处收压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:17.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,多亏他们  有钱买新鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,干了很多事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在家里躺着无所事事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  各有各的过法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:47.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能过来下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:50.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:56.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:58.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:08.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我问得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是滨口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:18.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,知道那家伙有没有什么想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他马上生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等等  你别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是他先送我礼物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是我要送他  只是回个礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明白没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道他想要啥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你们俩关系不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我听其他的女生说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北条最近似乎沉迷烤饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那家伙不擅长做吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:09.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我有点想尝尝呢  北条亲手做的曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他说想吃北条同学亲手做的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么那家伙会知道我迷上烤曲奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这  我不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那家伙  想吃我的曲奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  也没必要为他花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,滨口这种人  送他曲奇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再见  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这件事不要跟任何人提起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,午休时你跟北条说话来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我路过看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你们都说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不要跟任何人提起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也没说什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:21.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的是秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比如滨口同学想要什么东西  之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,隐约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我猜对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一如既往地敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我又不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片有什么想要的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:19.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我没有跟北条讨论这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟那个没关系  只是我好奇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:24.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想作为选礼物的参考
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要送谁礼物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大概是15岁的男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比我大一岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不不  可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么能总是上她的套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肯定又在说狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那只吉娃娃不是16岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是初三的男生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪  我还以为她又要来捉弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个…我不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再好好想一想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,额  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是关系到你自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是西片下个生日的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想好要什么礼物了就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:36.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么我会有松了一口气的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没能把我跟北条说的事告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为我跟人家约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我好像使坏过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你不是一直在使坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是一直捉弄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:33.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那…是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片送我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.94,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:15.74,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:19.41,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:24.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.61,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君が住む山は「スノーランド」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:36.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一年中雪の降るこの国で    私は生まれたのと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.48,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君は話してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.40,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ねぇ    私は夏を見たことがないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:56.36,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}燃えるようなあの夏を    それを見るのが私の夢なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:58.85,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}でも良いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:06.92,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}この世界は知らない方がロマンチックな事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:13.16,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}たくさんあるのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.16,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.99,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:24.65,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.77,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の精？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:37.17,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の妖精とのファンタジー
