Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:19.41,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我对你一见倾心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:24.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}难道你就是雪之妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.61,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你住在名为「雪国」的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:36.25,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}降生于终年飘雪的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.48,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你曾对我如是诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.40,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呐  我从未见过盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:56.36,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看那炽热如火的盛夏  是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:58.85,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不过无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:06.92,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在这个世界上还有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:13.16,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为未知才有的浪漫对吧
